div.span:
Create python env: '
Run python3 -m venv env'

Install python modules: '
Run pip install -r requirements.txt'

Run flask server: '
Run flask run'

Bundle JS files & Run flask server: '
Run npx webpack --config webpack.config.js
flask run'

Rebuild database & Run flask server: '
Run flask db init
flask db migrate
flask db upgrade
flask run'

Install deps, bundle JS & Run flask server: '
Run npm install -g parcel-bundler
npm i
npx webpack --config webpack.config.js
flask run'
